WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: jnaGY85MGyc

NOTE Language: en

00:00:05.680 --> 00:00:10.387
For example, the people who came
today they are living with unreal things.

00:00:10.467 --> 00:00:13.207
They have to seek God.

00:00:13.327 --> 00:00:17.283
If they follow any religion it is to seek God.

00:00:17.363 --> 00:00:23.083
If they are thinking they belong to any caste,

00:00:23.175 --> 00:00:28.197
community, anything which professes God, has to seek God.

00:00:28.278 --> 00:00:35.355
Even the people who are agnostic, those
people who are atheists have to seek the creator.

00:00:35.435 --> 00:00:39.530
One must know that you are not the creator.

00:00:39.611 --> 00:00:44.236
If once you know that you are not the
creator and when you start seeking that

00:00:44.316 --> 00:00:49.364
then you are a higher category of
a personality which I call as Seeker.

00:00:49.444 --> 00:00:55.267
For which William Blake has said clearly, “Men of God…

00:00:55.367 --> 00:01:01.498
Men of God will become prophets.

00:01:01.578 --> 00:01:05.577
And these prophets will have….
Prophets means again non-beings….

00:01:05.657 --> 00:01:09.715
have powers to make others prophets.

00:01:09.795 --> 00:01:14.510
Is already predicted. Your
potentiality has already been predicted.

00:01:14.590 --> 00:01:19.988
But if you have no value for your being,
you’re wasting it for nonsensical things

00:01:20.068 --> 00:01:23.330
then nobody can help you.

00:01:23.410 --> 00:01:29.371
Nobody can help a person who has no
sense in his head, who is wasting his energy.

00:01:29.451 --> 00:01:39.497
So one thing is important that Sahaja yoga is
only for the people who are seekers, to begin with.

00:01:39.597 --> 00:01:45.340
Those who are not, we are not bothered.

00:01:45.420 --> 00:01:49.229
We are not going to fall at their feet.

00:01:49.309 --> 00:01:54.544
We are not an organization or
anything. We do not want any money.

00:01:54.624 --> 00:02:00.117
We want to help people who
are seeking, to ascent that’s all.

00:02:00.197 --> 00:02:03.739
There is no need for them to come.

00:02:03.819 --> 00:02:07.189
There is…nobody has asked them to come.

00:02:07.269 --> 00:02:12.881
Like other cults are anxious to keep the people, we are not.

00:02:12.961 --> 00:02:18.585
The reason is there are two
forces all the time acting in nature

00:02:18.671 --> 00:02:22.967
which you must be knowing as
centrifugal and centripetal forces.

00:02:23.052 --> 00:02:27.738
By one force you are sucked in but
by another force, you are thrown out.

00:02:27.819 --> 00:02:31.803
If you are no good you are thrown out.
That’s how evolution has taken place.

00:02:31.884 --> 00:02:34.538
As you know that in evolutionary processes

00:02:34.618 --> 00:02:40.548
many animals many vegetables many plants
have been thrown out of the evolutionary process.

00:02:40.628 --> 00:02:45.120
In the same way, all such people are thrown out.

00:02:45.201 --> 00:02:49.732
So it makes no difference to the divine.

00:02:49.812 --> 00:02:54.668
If there are five people, well and good.
If there are thousands, well and good.

00:02:54.748 --> 00:03:04.043
But only a mother’s concern is such that after
all so many are created from amoeba to this level

00:03:04.123 --> 00:03:07.226
and there are so many seekers on this earth.

00:03:07.313 --> 00:03:12.131
They may be doing the wrong things. They
might be doing some things that are not proper.

00:03:12.211 --> 00:03:15.757
They might be mislaid doesn’t matter. Forgive them.

00:03:15.838 --> 00:03:23.558
But for them, it should be
available that they get their ascent.

00:03:23.658 --> 00:03:27.266
They should get their ascent. It should be available.

00:03:27.346 --> 00:03:33.391
That’s the only concern I have or any other Sahaja yogi has.

00:03:33.471 --> 00:03:37.835
He doesn’t care what money you have.
He doesn’t care what position you have.

00:03:37.915 --> 00:03:40.836
He doesn’t care for anything whatsoever.

00:03:41.323 --> 00:03:45.154
Only concern is that you are a seeker.

00:03:45.234 --> 00:03:48.718
And you have every right to ascent.

00:03:48.798 --> 00:03:52.864
And those who have ascended want to help you.

00:03:52.944 --> 00:03:57.599
Just to help you to ascent so
that you can help others to ascent.
